":{"pid":"79930fa0edb9411a2fe1b587c9e5d49deac953e5","tid":2069764,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e0845895d91283a997b9b08fe8a69d83e087566","tid":2069764,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6ea8a5d92876424b51fb1ef85e52503fbb8de8","tid":2069764,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63946ccec96bd14d01cd81b753a1fa2f6ea72df8","tid":2069764,"uid":97056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔一定要有啲咩症先可以尋求協助<br />\n最緊要係知道自己幾次到limit<br />\n好朋友社工counsellor甚至去搵診所醫生都可以<br />\n特別係搵醫生開少少安眠藥俾你去渡過最辛苦最訓唔到既時期可能會有好大幫助，個人夠訓精神狀態都會舒服好多<br />\n最緊要係搵人幫你！唔好自己死頂<br />\n好辛苦就俾自己頹下咩都唔做<br />\n電腦過熱都要reboot啦，我哋個腦都一樣<br />\n唔清楚你咩狀況都俾唔到咩安慰你<br />\n希望你搵到第二朝起身既勇氣"},{"pid":"6ddd1de9f34eedfb0620e2c705437d4405d7194f","tid":2069764,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc7b10faa906ba7d7de092e2e56a5eab6b783cc","tid":2069764,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=ffd66fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"68f036f9ef6093b42d669db142c3c9893fe36b07","tid":2069764,"uid":145292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b1ff2248dabd5fb1e92aa5087bff5c5754b494e","tid":2069764,"uid":336070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:49:23.000Z","msg":"我有一段時間都係咁，仲會一到夜晚就會無啦啦喺度喊到收唔到聲，每晚都係喊到攰到訓著先訓到教，其他人只會叫你唔好諗野咁悲觀啦要正面啲，但問題係我自己真係控制唔到，時間耐咗我就連野都唔想再同人講，因為根本都冇人明，寧願自己匿埋唔開心喊到攰就訓，聽朝醒就另一日先再算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5a69895bd5ce0a8652dba960f0c18c394b3305","tid":2069764,"uid":191094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:22:30.000Z","msg":"我唔識點樣去安慰你<br />\n不過我覺得唔開心嘅時候<br />\n最大嘅安慰係知道有人同自己處境一樣<br />\nyou are not alone<br />\n之前都有人開過類似嘅post<br />\n希望你睇完過來人分享會覺得多d力量<br />\n或者揾個信得過嘅朋友傾下"},{"pid":"da807b287f8cb5e1a0e8413a5a37c904edfe42c0","tid":2069764,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"你係咪黎M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71994541a69f856dbcbb0dd3688fbe0dfeecb581","tid":2069764,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1ff2248dabd5fb1e92aa5087bff5c5754b494e","tid":2069764,"uid":336070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:49:23.000Z","msg":"我有一段時間都係咁，仲會一到夜晚就會無啦啦喺度喊到收唔到聲，每晚都係喊到攰到訓著先訓到教，其他人只會叫你唔好諗野咁悲觀啦要正面啲，但問題係我自己真係控制唔到，時間耐咗我就連野都唔想再同人講，因為根本都冇人明，寧願自己匿埋唔開心喊到攰就訓，聽朝醒就另一日先再算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />same<br />\n個人感覺到自己係down<br />\n唔想同人講都唔知自己因為咩事而down<br />\n唔識講唔想講都冇一個合適嘅人講<br />\n你知啦<br />\n你講左d人一係好簡單叫你唔好唔開心啦<br />\n乜都冇解決過<br />\n一係話你平時唔係咁個喎 <br />\n冇重視過呢個問題<br />\n咁算啦<br />\n我都唔知應該點<br />\n然後又自己匿埋收收埋埋"},{"pid":"e0f661fa30c4a777ec7e77b81f3900c69e567117","tid":2069764,"uid":6473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:49:01.000Z","msg":"我都有呢種感覺<br />\n持續咗好多年 <br />\n啱啱仲分開咗 <br />\n覺得唔多唔少都係因為咁<br />\n因為會好容易情緒低落<br />\n然後想最可以依靠嘅人幫到自己<br />\n將情緒轉化咗俾佢<br />\n好辛苦 好後悔<br />\n依家個感覺一係死一係睇醫生<br />\n冇辦法"},{"pid":"6079a561819512084af0f2a52f58810eb32a7f6c","tid":2069764,"uid":279814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T20:22:34.000Z","msg":"[url]好明 唉[/url]"},{"pid":"925ba566aaf64adb665215bcff65b8653b36624f","tid":2069764,"uid":11075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6ea8a5d92876424b51fb1ef85e52503fbb8de8","tid":2069764,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115a89c253196b71d45f26224ce6dabd6c20ae7f","tid":2069764,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f151e811684119682d66a049157291670ff97a","tid":2069764,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"首先樓主你唔好改個咁嘅名先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住呢個username真係冇事都亂諗嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e53e04c917f34b3395264a1e6eda1780eb4d0f4","tid":2069764,"uid":319312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"我試過持續兩年<br />\n奉勸樓主快啲求助<br />\n唔係嘅話會一發不可收拾"},{"pid":"6b8f369103cfc0e62536c6fce26773beb7b8917c","tid":2069764,"uid":354503,"like":0,